title: Trials and Confessions of a Housekeeper
creator: T. S. Arthur
description: LibriVox recording of Trials and Confessions of a Housekeeper, by T. S. Arthur. Read by Kehinde. Is housekeeping such a trial? Mrs. Smith thinks so and confesses all in this merry account of her escapades and near disasters! (Summary by Kehinde) For further information, including links to M4B audio book, online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
